{"tid":1298823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［同我入黎］撤回兩個字係咪真係咁重要？！！","createTime":"2019-07-09T02:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:34:52.000Z","uid":249040,"like":52,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cde6a64cda7373fc2621017a8b7f16dbce1c4621","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求之中你林奠你知道「撤回」呢一項個門檻最低，而你亦唔準備答應其他四大，你都唔肯講<br />\n<br />\n失去左咁多烈士生命， 你都唔肯講<br />\n<br />\n你話知道帶俾大家幾多傷害、見到幾多深層次矛盾同撕裂，但你都唔肯講<br />\n<br />\n你寧願講壽終正寢the bill is dead，都唔肯講，代表乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代表到宜家，就算你全軍覆沒眾叛親離，你都擺自己面子重要過大家嘅民意、血汗、甚至生命！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n剩係呢點！<br />\n<br />\n我堅決唔收貨！<br />\n<br />\n繼續堅守定落黎嘅訴求！<br />\n <br />\n未敢忘記612，71，77！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e18aa772f9c31ab24f2b798fd01c88bc17747523","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34dd2b849bb8b05c6a4e267cefb57bd45d16ecdf","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ce5c2421500ebd300003521b06aef95bdc662de","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"306916de87377ceda6851ca86614326feaa3bf9e","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0aacb4e2b118b8e50f27225a5e7e1e3467fcabff","tid":1298823,"uid":272553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16dd1b3c5d602ce388f6b1e45d9ae5710ff54656","tid":1298823,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩=可以一再搞就二讀開始搞<br />\n撤回=要從頭諮詢、一讀開始搞</span></span>"},{"pid":"69da522fb0c62cd0cdeb61da6a827b22b125957c","tid":1298823,"uid":205043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"勿忘清拆皇后碼頭教訓"},{"pid":"68040486347b619e7b709313c39fb9851cc55ad7","tid":1298823,"uid":82492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"不撤不散"},{"pid":"cbe429714cf1636f5b365cbc87a8cd9d5df0e87f","tid":1298823,"uid":122389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">64. 法案的撤回或押後處理 \n\n(1) 負責某法案的議員或官員，可在立法會開始就該法案進行二讀或三讀的程序時，宣布撤回或押後處理該法案。 \n(2005年第74號法律公告) \n\n(2) 負責某法案的議員或官員可在符合以下條件的情況下，在立法會開始就該法案進行恢復二讀辯論的程序時，宣布撤回該法案 - \n\n(a) 恢復二讀辯論的目的是為了作出該項宣布；及 \n\n(b) 該目的已在根據本議事規則第54(5)條(二讀)作出恢復二讀辯論的預告中述明。\n(2005年第74號法律公告) \n\n(3) 負責某法案的議員或官員在根據第(2)款宣布撤回該法案時，可就與撤回該法案有關的事宜向立法會發言，但該等發言不容辯論。 (2005年第74號法律公告) </code></pre>"},{"pid":"5b93d7e48fd8670bc02950d1250562b07fd13bc0","tid":1298823,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xa6COxw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXa6COxw.png&h=d9f523d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce20fba10a9dff4ef46f602175a5bfb5c2ee92e","tid":1298823,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:50:19.000Z","msg":"仆街林鄭 玩語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdad9fcc15b9746ce822663730ac7b3723c555d5","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9266df3631bf1950ddf15b5d706ee4f0e16d37e2","tid":1298823,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6867b895c38ae122efddccf408771c71edbc32fa","tid":1298823,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike"